item.title: Tsukuyomii Village, The Village Hidden in The Moon
item.content:encoded:
hello everyone in BvS land…
i am the kage of a new village and i need members
i don't have NRF yet or any other upgrade really.
will be getting the party house tomorrow at day roll providing the fact that i can get our resource.
but either way we will have it soon
if you are looking for a good time i hope to see you there.
well everyone…i hope you consider joining me and our adventure in the Tsukuyomii village
and if not good luck you all.
thanks for your consideration.
Sincerly,
Pupp
